    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nCodelenses are not very discoverable (do we enable them by default?). \n\n### Expected behavior\n\nThe `gra` mapping should iterate through available codelenses (presumably via `vim.lsp.codelens.get()`) and include them in the menu (possibly with a `(codelense)` hint suffix in the menu item).\n\n### Related:\n\n- https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/32606",
    "closed_at": null,
    "closed_by": {
        "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2361214?v=4",
        "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/clason/events{/privacy}",
