        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "They're not enabled by default, and I don't think we should. Not even VS Code does.\n\nI'm not a fan of the idea of the idea of combining code actions and lenses. I do think that we should have default mappings for it though.\n\nMaybe something to consider is a new combined UI (and mapping) that would contain results for code actions, lenses, and inlay hint commands. For the latter 2 interactivity is normally done by clicking on other editors.",
